<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 12:27:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>如何检测超光速旅行</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/how-to-detect-faster-than-light-travel</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 12:27:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/how-to-detect-faster-than-light-travel</guid></item><item><title>了解有关 NordVPN 的更多信息：</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/learn-more-about-nordvpn-at</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 12:12:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/learn-more-about-nordvpn-at</guid></item><item><title>为什么信息不能被销毁——Leonard Susskind</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/why-information-cannot-be-destroyed-leonard-susskind</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 11:57:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/why-information-cannot-be-destroyed-leonard-susskind</guid></item><item><title>大脑成瘾回路被发现！</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/brains-addiction-circuit-identified</link><description>当兴奋性信号和抑制性信号处于平衡状态时，我们大脑的前额叶皮层（PFC）可以适当地发挥其“制动”功能来抑制冲动。为了研究长期接触药物如何破坏这种平衡，研究小组对小鼠进行了可卡因给药实验。在此过程中，他们追踪了前额皮质中的抑制性神经元何时被激活以及它们如何向下游大脑区域发送信号。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/brains-addiction-circuit-identified2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 11:42:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/brains-addiction-circuit-identified</guid></item><item><title>老水手神话卫星实际证实是真的</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-old-sailor-myth-satellites-actually-confirmed-is-true</link><description>借助最新的卫星数据，我们观察到了波高巨大的风暴，可能高出海面 100 英尺以上。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-old-sailor-myth-satellites-actually-confirmed-is-true.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 11:27:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-old-sailor-myth-satellites-actually-confirmed-is-true</guid></item><item><title>错配修复缺陷产生的胞质DNA结构协调结直肠癌的抗肿瘤免疫</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/cytosolic-dna-structures-produced-by-mismatch-repair-deficiency-coordinate-anti-tumor-immunity-in-colorectal-cancer</link><description>莫斯利等人。研究细胞质 DNA 结构在 MSI 结直肠癌激活 cGAS/STING 中的作用。他们发现 MSI 胞质 DNA 富含 G-四链体，从而导致更有效的 cGAS/STING 激活。微核通过 cGAS/STING 激活细胞毒性 T 细胞的效果较差，但会增加 IL-10 和 Treg 的激活。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/cytosolic-dna-structures-produced-by-mismatch-repair-deficiency-coordinate-anti-tumor-immunity-in-colorectal-cancer.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 11:12:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/cytosolic-dna-structures-produced-by-mismatch-repair-deficiency-coordinate-anti-tumor-immunity-in-colorectal-cancer</guid></item><item><title>肥胖间歇性禁食期间，胰岛素和脂肪细胞 IRF4 促进脂肪保留而不是肌肉保存</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/insulin-and-adipocyte-irf4-promote-fat-retention-over-muscle-preservation-during-intermittent-fasting-in-obesity</link><description>马尔科等人。研究表明，肥胖小鼠体内胰岛素升高会抑制脂肪细胞 IRF4，而 IRF4 在 5:2 间歇性禁食 (IF) 期间控制脂肪与肌肉的保存，无论是否限制热量。在人类急性禁食期间，肥胖和胰岛素升高会促进男性瘦体重的减少，但不会促进女性瘦体重的减少。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/insulin-and-adipocyte-irf4-promote-fat-retention-over-muscle-preservation-during-intermittent-fasting-in-obesity2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 10:57:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/insulin-and-adipocyte-irf4-promote-fat-retention-over-muscle-preservation-during-intermittent-fasting-in-obesity</guid></item><item><title>对于预防和管理慢性电解质失衡引起的矿物质和骨骼疾病非常重要👇</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/important-for-the-prevention-and-management-of-mineral-and-bone-disorders-from-chronic-electrolyte-imbalance%f0%9f%91%87</link><description>https://doi.org/10.1172/jci.insight &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/important-for-the-prevention-and-management-of-mineral-and-bone-disorders-from-chronic-electrolyte-imbalancef09f9187.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 10:42:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/important-for-the-prevention-and-management-of-mineral-and-bone-disorders-from-chronic-electrolyte-imbalance%f0%9f%91%87</guid></item><item><title>万福玛丽计划的推测演变</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-speculative-evolution-of-project-hail-mary</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 10:27:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-speculative-evolution-of-project-hail-mary</guid></item><item><title>World Creator 2026.3 现在允许您使用真实世界的高程数据</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/world-creator-2026-3-now-allows-you-to-use-real-world-elevation-data</link><description>您将能够更好地控制场景、放置对象和使用以前的预设。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/world-creator-2026-3-now-allows-you-to-use-real-world-elevation-data.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 10:12:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/world-creator-2026-3-now-allows-you-to-use-real-world-elevation-data</guid></item></channel></rss>